  "texts": [
    "Next, we conduct a Wilcoxon signed-rank test to assess whether the mean and median prestige scores are statistically different.",
    "The results are presented below.",
    "The test statistic value is 73636.5 with a p-value of 0.226, indicating that there is no significant difference between the mean and median prestige scores at a conventional significance level of 0.05.",
    "The test was conducted under the two-sided alternative hypothesis, which checks for differences in either direction.",
    "X Table A2."
  ]
}